Z15094.description: Besha yearned for land, while Arina wished to know more about the sea, hoping to get new ideas for her art.

Z15214.name: Rabbit Vision
Z15214.description: Glasses were also essential. Cicely had a dozen rabbit-eye-shaped glasses in her drawer!

Z15406.name: Olden Memories
Z15406.description: Ayesha gazed into Jafar's eyes and remembered a song that had never been played, written by the chieftain's wife.

Z15413.name: Foregone Memory
Z15413.description: Beneath the stars, they talk on and on, knowing that they'd become good friends without having to confirm.

Z15574.name: Spotless Gaze
Z15574.description: 'It's over.' the mother touched the girl's cheeks, 'Princess Youell's courage brought warmth and light to the night.'

Z15656.name: Delicate Dream
Z15656.description: The other Morino grinned and started chanting the same spell. Their voices overlapped into one in the empty room.

Z15667.name: Silent Vestige
Z15667.description: The girl lingered, never harming a soul, so Hetta enveloped her in a bundle of energy to keep her from fading away.

Z15726.name: Dewdrop Aroma
Z15726.description: It's said that when Shuji passed away, all the peonies bloomed. She is remembered as the Peony Goddess even now.

Z16039.name: Crystalline Frost
Z16039.description: The girl spent all day preparing flowers for others to offer the Goddess and missed the festival herself.
